Class DestroyedEntityEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • communication.messages.Message
      • communication.messages.events.entity.DestroyedEntityEvent
  • public class DestroyedEntityEvent
extends Message
    This message is sent when an entity is removed from the map. This does not mean that the entity doesn't exist anymore, but the entity might be placed in the inventory of a character if it is an Infinity Stone
